description: Li3 Lithium Corp. focuses on the exploration and development of lithium properties. It holds interest in the Mutare lithium project that covers an area of 1,500 hectares located within the Mutare Greenstone Belt of Zimbabwe. The company was formerly known as Western Troy Capital Resources Inc. and changed its name to Li3 Lithium Corp. in August 2022. Li3 Lithium Corp. was incorporated in 1988 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Francois  Auclair F.G.A.C., geologist, M.Sc., P.Geo., PGeo
